Source: duckbotos-kiosk-openclaw
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: DuckBotOS Team <duckets@duckbotos.dev>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: duckbotos-kiosk-openclaw
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: duckbotos-kiosk,
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pre-configure DuckBotOS kiosk for OpenClaw workspace
 Configures /etc/duckbotos/kiosk-mode to load the OpenClaw workspace
 (http://localhost:18789/plugins/openclawos) when the kiosk starts.
 .
 This package conflicts with duckbotos-kiosk-hermes — installing one
 deconfigures the other.
Conflicts: duckbotos-kiosk-hermes
